---
import "./Bath.css";
---
<section class="prices">
    <h2 class="prices__title">
        How Much Does a Bathroom<br />Remodel Cost in Maryland?
    </h2>
    <div class="prices__desc">
        See the average investment by bathroom size — and what's included in each remodel. If you're planning to remodel your bathroom in Maryland, it's important to understand the typical investment based on bathroom size and features. Whether you're updating a small powder room or doing a full master bath transformation, this guide gives you a general price range — and what's usually included at each level.
        <br /><br />
        <span class="prices__note">
      *Prices shown are estimates and may vary depending on materials, finishes, plumbing work, structural changes, and overall project complexity.
    </span>
    </div>
    <div class="prices__tiers">
        <!-- Small Bathroom -->
        <div class="prices__tier">
            <img src="public/BathroomPage/bath5.png" alt="Small Bathroom" class="prices__img" />
            <div class="prices__tier-title">Small Bathroom</div>
            <div class="prices__tier-sub">Under 40 ft²</div>
            <div class="prices__tier-price">$8,000 – $15,000*</div>
            <div class="prices__tier-desc">
                Ideal for half baths and guest bathrooms.
                <ul>
                    <li>Space-saving layouts</li>
                    <li>Compact vanities & toilets</li>
                    <li>Standard tile & waterproof flooring</li>
                    <li>Basic lighting & plumbing upgrades</li>
                </ul>
                Functional and stylish upgrades for limited space.
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Medium Bathroom -->
        <div class="prices__tier">
            <img src="public/BathroomPage/bath6.png" alt="Medium Bathroom" class="prices__img" />
            <div class="prices__tier-title">Medium Bathroom</div>
            <div class="prices__tier-sub">40 – 80 ft²</div>
            <div class="prices__tier-price">$15,000 – $25,000*</div>
            <div class="prices__tier-desc">
                Common in townhomes and standard-size homes.
                <ul>
                    <li>Custom vanity & storage</li>
                    <li>Walk-in shower or tub-shower combo</li>
                    <li>High-quality tilework & fixtures</li>
                    <li>Lighting & ventilation improvements</li>
                </ul>
                Balanced design for comfort, function, and elegance.
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Master Bath -->
        <div class="prices__tier">
            <img src="public/BathroomPage/bath7.png" alt="Master Bath" class="prices__img" />
            <div class="prices__tier-title">Master Bath</div>
            <div class="prices__tier-sub">Over 80 ft²</div>
            <div class="prices__tier-price">$25,000 – $45,000+*</div>
            <div class="prices__tier-desc">
                Luxurious layouts with room for upgrades.
                <ul>
                    <li>Freestanding tub & walk-in shower</li>
                    <li>Dual vanities & premium fixtures</li>
                    <li>Heated flooring & smart lighting</li>
                    <li>Designer finishes & full customization</li>
                </ul>
                Transform your bathroom into a spa-like retreat.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="prices__cta-wrap">
        <a href="#" class="prices__cta">Request your free quote →</a>
    </div>
</section>